{"tid":1737121,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港曾經有咩違憲審查嘅案？","createTime":"2019-11-19T01:19:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T16:40:57.000Z","uid":71237,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"bb008a808ca640b1761a3e4618ab7d899c814ef3","tid":1737121,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T01:19:02.000Z","msg":"今日大家都睇到全國人大話「特區法律是否符合基本法，只能由全國人大決定」。<br />\n我就想查下香港曾經有咩違憲審查的案。<br />\n<br />\n然後我見到維基百科有香港違憲審查案件列表<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%81%95%E6%86%B2%E5%AF%A9%E6%9F%A5%E6%A1%88%E4%BB%B6%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%2581%2595%25E6%2586%25B2%25E5%25AF%25A9%25E6%259F%25A5%25E6%25A1%2588%25E4%25BB%25B6%25E5%2588%2597%25E8%25A1%25A8&d=uyJPOiOY0yV7leae1MMhfAjMvzJQG4GdM8cyRMJzdLg%3D&h=76c9f02b\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%81%95%E6%86%B2%E5%AF%A9%E6%9F%A5%E6%A1%88%E4%BB%B6%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8</a><br />\n<br />\n但係個表好耐無update，2008年嘅案仲話打緊。<br />\n有冇熟悉法律嘅人可以講下香港仲有咩違憲審查案件？"},{"pid":"2a3d3c98401bfed08f11f35a1dc95356ab787259","tid":1737121,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T01:44:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"46c1c376a123690fddb881725a8dbd1211203ef9","tid":1737121,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T03:01:32.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"37a3fe8ed0157bae7acfe133215ff2e6840181bb","tid":1737121,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T03:44:33.000Z","msg":"推呀<br />\n普及下大家的認知都好呀"},{"pid":"4562a224ff5432b46e0a4b276ca9020d4b2cdade","tid":1737121,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T16:40:57.000Z","msg":"推"}]}